they have a youth, glamour and pizazz and they preserve a longstanding tradition,'' he said
today, andrew and sarah were to take a tour of showscan, a movie special effects studio in suburban culver city. later, they planned to meet with british oscar winners at the academy of motion picture arts and sciences in beverly hills
