scott appeared in broadway companies of ``king of hearts'' and ``dancin.'' on television he performed in ``baryshnikov in hollywood'' and during the 1980 academy awards broadcast
scott also had a small part in the film version of ``a chorus line.'' in 1982, he auditioned for the role of mr. mistoffelees and stayed with ``cats'' for about 18 months
