decisions made by the louisiana district presbytery today will be returned to the executive presbytery. there will be no further announcement or comment from the louisiana district council,'' janway said
there was no indication whether swaggart attended that meeting, which lasted from 10 a.m. to 7 p.m. the rev. jim rentz, who is substituting for swaggart at the family worship center in baton rouge, attended the meeting
